data.description: Welcome home to 304 Brentford Dr, located in the highly sought after Canterbury Farms subdivision. This beautiful 5 bed, 3 bath home has been well-maintained and is ready for it's new owner! It has a new roof, UV system for better air quality, and hardwired to use a generator. This gorgeous home boasts an open floor plan, gourmet-style eat in kitchen with granite countertops, bar, and pantry, formal dining room, hardwood floors through main living area, exceptional master suite that includes double vanities, garden tub, separate shower, granite countertops, and huge walk-in closet, privacy fenced back yard, screened in apoxy back patio, firepit, double car garage, and SO MUCH MORE! You don't want to miss this one!
